lead_paragraph: Japan's women's football team, former world champions, failed to qualify for the Rio Olympics as Australia and China booked the two available spots in the Asian qualifiers for the tournament.

headline.print_headline: Japan Women Miss Out on Rio Football as Australia, China Go Through
